videos.description: Cole Anthony gets into the teeth of Syracuse's zone and floats up a lob to Garrison Brooks for the alley-oop connection.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony lobs to Brooks for UNC alley-oop) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Anthony lobs to Brooks for UNC alley-oop

videos.description: Former Syracuse star John Wallace has his number raised into the rafters at the Carrier Dome during a halftime ceremony.
videos.headline: Syracuse retires John Wallace's number

videos.description: North Carolina comes out on fire from deep in the second half, connecting on six 3-pointers in the first six minutes of action.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UNC lights up Cuse's zone to start 2nd half) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: UNC lights up Cuse's zone to start 2nd half

videos.description: Jimmy Fallon gets Syracuse fans on their feet by leading the team's pep band during a timeout.
videos.headline: Jimmy Fallon conducts Syracuse band

videos.description: Cole Anthony stays hot from outside, knocking down shots from deep on consecutive possessions for his sixth and seventh 3-pointers of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony buries back-to-back triples for UNC) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Anthony buries back-to-back triples for UNC
